<br>
Allow me to introduce myself...<br>
<br>
I am Malagis(x) Windrider<br>
55 Evoker<br>
AE Prophet of Gnomallah<br>
The Hand<br>
Xev<br>
<br>
Just wanted to BUMP! this thread. This is flat out the best tactic there is, and is only limited by your audacity. <br>
<br>
Yes it works at low levels (my enchanter and a friends Mage do this in Kerra at 17 currently, and we plan to continue to 60 primarily doing AE)<br>
<br>
Current records for groups I was in:<br>
<br>
Most damage one cast:<br>
23x 854 (19472) in Lower Guk (Bard Pull)<br>
<br>
Most damage one pull:<br>
19 frogs scarabs and iksar in Old Sebilis Chef area, included 5 Krups i dont have exact numbers, but was probably around 100k damage total in less than 120 secs.<br>
<br>
The only places you CANT do this are giants and other unmezzable mob areas.<br>
<br>
Get adventurous. Mages make an Awesome 3rd nuker, because in addition to very nice AE damage with the Flux line and Scint, your Pets are perfect for finishing that last stubborn Named mob off. BTW yes mana efficiency &gt; than speed. Chanter uses less mana than anyone else in the group.<br>
<br>
My perfect AE group *note this is a major dream*<br>
<br>
60 enchanter (group c2 and gift of brilliance)<br>
60 Bard (DA Song /owns)<br>
60 Druid (PotG and Pet)<br>
60 Wizard (with epic)<br>
60 Wizard (with epic)<br>
Any level mage who has managed to obtain the epic pet (see i told ya it was a dream, we feel for ya, we really do...)<br>
<br>
And HS is a great zone for AE, mostly cause everywhere else you run out of mobs too soon due to overcamping. The key is DA, and or Bardic Charm. As soon as the HTs have been unloaded these mobs are cake.<br>
<br>
So sally forth and slay!~ In large groups preferably...<br>
<br>
And if you play on Xev and want to try give me a tell, I'll add you to the AE friends list.<br>
<br>
For any of you younger folks that want to try, my Enchanter's name is Atlaar.<br>
<br>
See ya in game!<br>
<br>
Malagis <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#dcdeed><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub6.ezboard.com/ujayteebushwacker.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Jaytee Bushwacker</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Elementalist</span><br>  Posts: 71<br> <font color=#333333>(8/27/01 4:14:55 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub102.ezboard.com/fthemagicianstowerlibrarysubmissions.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=53.topic&index=33>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title>   Re: 12,000 damages in one nuke ?</span><hr size=1> I have to congratulate you my fellow mage =)  I have also know the glory of the AE group on the Veeshan server.  My personal record is 21 dead froggies in a single pull.  <br>
